OL,3,CSouthampton 'Spygate' hearing may not
OL,4,Ctake place until Tuesday
OL,6,FSpying charges against Southampton may
OL,7,Fnot be heard until Tuesday (19 May),
OL,8,Fplacing a question mark over the
OL,9,Fscheduling of next week's Championship
OL,10,Fplay-off final.
OL,12,FThe club were charged last week by the
OL,13,FEFL with spying on a training session
OL,14,Fheld by semi-final opponents
OL,15,FMiddlesbrough, with the league asking
OL,16,Ffor an independent commission to
OL,17,Fexamine the case "at the earliest
OL,18,Fopportunity".
OL,26,@yD@ROUzD@LO]
