PN,42302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1778789155
OL,3,CSouthampton 'Spygate' hearing may not
OL,4,Ctake place until Tuesday
OL,6,FThe EFL issued a statement on Thursday
OL,7,F(14 May) afternoon to say the hearing
OL,8,Fwould take place "on or before
OL,9,FTuesday, May 19".
OL,11,FGiven the high stakes involved, an
OL,12,Fappeal from one or more parties in the
OL,13,Fcase seems almost certain, putting a
OL,14,Fquestion mark over whether the appeal
OL,15,Fcould be heard before the date
OL,16,Fscheduled for the final, 23 May, if
OL,17,Fthe initial hearing does not happen
OL,18,Funtil Tuesday.
OL,26,@pD@ROUqD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1778789155
OL,3,CSouthampton 'Spygate' hearing may not
OL,4,Ctake place until Tuesday
OL,6,FHowever, the EFL said it "continues to
OL,7,Fplan on the basis that the
OL,8,FChampionship play-off final will take
OL,9,Fplace as scheduled".
OL,11,FThe EFL said the match was scheduled
OL,12,Fto kick off at 4.30pm.
OL,14,FThe EFL, which was at pains to point
OL,15,Fout that it did not have control of
OL,16,Fthe timetable due to the independent
OL,17,Fnature of the hearing, said the exact
OL,18,Fdate for the hearing "remains under
OL,19,Fdiscussion" and is expected to be
OL,20,Fconfirmed shortly.
OL,26,@nD@ZOUqD@SO]zD@VOU{D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
