FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1778789155
OL,3,CSouthampton 'Spygate' hearing may not
OL,4,Ctake place until Tuesday
OL,6,FWhile the league continues to plan for
OL,7,F23 May, it admitted: "Supporters
OL,8,Fshould, however, be aware that the
OL,9,Foutcome of the disciplinary
OL,10,Fproceedings may yet result in changes
OL,11,Fto the fixture."
OL,13,FThe league added that it has "a number
OL,14,Fof contingency plans should they be
OL,15,Frequired".
OL,17,FThe EFL said Hull and Southampton will
OL,18,Fshare further information on their
OL,19,Frespective sales processes later on
OL,20,FThursday.
OL,26,@oD@VOUsD@PO]uD@^OUwD@IO]
